text: Almenara can refer to: * Almenara, Minas Gerais, a city in Brazil * Almenara, Castellón, a municipality in Castellón province, Spain * Almenara de Adaja, a municipality in Valladolid province, Spain * Almenara de Tormes, a municipality in Salamanca province, Spain * Puebla de Almenara, a municipality in Cuenca province, Spain * Almenara (Madrid), a neighborhood in the district of Tetuán, in the municipality of Madrid, Community of Madrid, Spain * Pico Almenara, the highest mountain of Sierra de Alcaraz, Spain ==See also== * Battle of Almenar, a battle in Spain fought 1710
title: Almenara
